{"tid":641419,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[VR體驗安樂死] Sarco 安樂死儀器，可以先用 VR 感受死亡前一刻","createTime":"2018-04-25T03:50:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-26T06:11:17.000Z","uid":160807,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"83f372a40dff5705fa91a30baacfd5cd8e9aa394","tid":641419,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T03:50:53.000Z","msg":"對於長期在疾病中痛苦不堪的人來說，他們現在能找到了一種痛快的解脫辦法。那還得益於倡導安樂死的設計師 Philip Nitschke ，他於上週在荷蘭阿姆斯特丹舉行的國際殯儀展用 VR 向人們展示了 Sarco 安樂死儀器。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/sarco.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2Fsarco.jpg&h=f9e53495&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這部 3D打印概念原型安樂死儀器 Sarco，被其設計者自稱為倡導「自願安樂死和理性自殺」的人權活動家 ，看似一艘飛船，原型是一個安置在傾斜支架上正常人尺寸的艙體，只要按下艙體內按鍵可立即填充氮氣。參展者更設置了一個 VR 眼罩，參觀的遊客可以 VR 方式，感受按下死亡按鈕時的感覺。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/543434543543345.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F543434543543345.jpg&h=2a16ff1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對於它的設計和用法， Philip Nitschke 對法新社強調說那些希望安樂死的人可以按壓按鍵，膠囊艙體會充滿氮氣，在一瞬間暈眩後艙內的人會立即喪失意識，無痛苦地死去 。<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">他還進一步地解釋說這不僅是對於末期病患和藥物中毒者，任何人都有權選擇結束生命的方式，而安樂死是非常人道的死亡方式。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/534545354444.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F534545354444.jpg&h=14db6a65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾時來香港展覽<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://qooah.com/2018/04/20/sarco-death-machine/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2018%2F04%2F20%2Fsarco-death-machine%2F&d=%2FajnvZ3LkmvwMiyJH2oijFzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=33be2737\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2018/04/20/sarco-death-machine/</a>"},{"pid":"5dae66476b32f2a6c09c8fd2ad5e332f6fc5e296","tid":641419,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T04:13:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2bfbd37256adcaff78c32a9e3fae2bf487388e8","tid":641419,"uid":37458,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T04:17:02.000Z","msg":"香港落單未<br />\n要訂幾多部"},{"pid":"9aa4a2a27bb00fa41c5122efe09e1d9457dfd4c4","tid":641419,"uid":38671,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T04:18:21.000Z","msg":"21世紀十大發明"},{"pid":"e4337645a7700d5077b6d105f6ca50fe002b9850","tid":641419,"uid":20227,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T04:36:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9605d04a02312c5c4378bf88e051d28fbeffcee8","tid":641419,"uid":42469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T04:42:31.000Z","msg":"唔明點解要搞部VR，㩒咗掣嗰VR會有咩特別嘢睇？"},{"pid":"e6b08ff48dee4bcc6b9aac19613571a0c6657239","tid":641419,"uid":63154,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T04:51:17.000Z","msg":"黎到香港放嚮路邊，用app掃QR code扣錢使用，共享安落死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c96449d6d1e9a121821e77647d086d20e142b88","tid":641419,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T23:21:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2c97bd68376dea0b015ee819e1cab8802f63230","tid":641419,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9605d04a02312c5c4378bf88e051d28fbeffcee8","tid":641419,"uid":42469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T04:42:31.000Z","msg":"唔明點解要搞部VR，㩒咗掣嗰VR會有咩特別嘢睇？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T23:32:32.000Z","msg":"用VR試一次操作過程"},{"pid":"35ab50d18286a6115eb8f5dd81c54bfb162d7e9d","tid":641419,"uid":55548,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T01:16:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=